Version:        2.5.0
Release:        0
Summary:        Generic VESA video driver for the Xorg X server
License:        MIT
Group:          System/X11/Servers/XF86_4
URL:            https://xorg.freedesktop.org/
Source0:        https://xorg.freedesktop.org/releases/individual/driver/%{name}-%{version}.tar.bz2
